**Overview**
This dashboard provides an overview of the issues ingested from Github.

The dashboard provides details on issues that are open and resolved. It provides a view of the top 10 repositories with issues. It also calculates the mean-time to fix (or close) an issue. The dashboard presents a view of top labels that are assigned to the issues. Finally, it gives a layout of top users creating and fixing the issues.
